{"tid":1451054,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我有方法 令警犬日日番工唔安樂(日常反警犬大行動)","createTime":"2019-08-11T18:17:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T12:10:01.000Z","uid":264983,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ee0d6225bc1bbfb28b54854bf9ccd6bff9d0fda1","tid":1451054,"uid":264983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:17:04.000Z","msg":"我P牌仔真係都忍唔住啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n由今日起，我宣布<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">和理非街邊燃狗行動</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">正式開始。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n希望大家每次出街，帶定一啲警察傷害平民(射頭 元朗警黑合作之類) 既大張相，印出黎，見到警察，任何一個，拎比佢地睇，再質問佢地：<br />\n<br />\n問佢 721 元朗佢地係邊，<br />\n荃灣斬人 你啲同胞係邊，<br />\n淨係識得對住靚仔蛇頭，<br />\n良心喺邊度，之類之類。<br />\n<br />\n最少兩人一組，一人扮問路，突然攞呢啲宣傳出黎，再質問佢地，另一個開Facebook live 影住佢地。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">等全部人都知佢地幾醜樣</span><br />\n<br />\n拋磚引玉，希望師兄隨便修改，<br />\n<br />\n唔好畀佢番工咁好受"},{"pid":"78ce7d31d471e4ba2312a4fe5f6bb25496e169b2","tid":1451054,"uid":264983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:17:57.000Z","msg":"自推10"},{"pid":"133cd4b0773ee5055febfe31f79e45bf05d0fd95","tid":1451054,"uid":264983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:18:14.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"f501ee861e25ef6641700b02b0686d0132558c45","tid":1451054,"uid":264983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:18:30.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"83a5cf5cb70bde83d29ea8b41ef34bbfeb65a2f5","tid":1451054,"uid":264983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:18:52.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"fa6ea6406038e621f7af23bcd5ac7a4ea8bd8047","tid":1451054,"uid":264983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:19:21.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"efa304f947c7485015cf78c3a1fa48d2b5c32bb9","tid":1451054,"uid":264983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"